  <title>17 Best Things To Do in Kanazawa (2026 Japan Guide)</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Planning a trip to Kanazawa? Our 2026 local guide covers the 17 best things to do — Kenroku-en garden, Higashi Chaya geisha district, 21st Century Museum & hidden temples. Skip-the-line tips included." />
